{"tid":1760138,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對黑警嘅仇恨一定要延續落去，成個社會摒棄孤立佢地","createTime":"2019-11-28T04:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:17:53.000Z","uid":120847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ccfd848d795eaf4871e6d85fe386f875c6efa6","tid":1760138,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"區選嘅勝利已經令大家對黑警嘅仇恨淡化<br />\n大家係咪已經原諒左黑警?<br />\n<br />\n721完全無視市民性命安危<br />\n平日以殘害無辜市民為樂，暴力成癮<br />\n完全泯滅人性<br />\n甚至試圖奪權建立軍政府<br />\n呢個與民為敵嘅武裝組織，任何一個有血性嘅人都唔可以忘記佢地嘅所作所為<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要讓仇恨延續下去，<br />\n直至佢地被清算，被唾棄，被毀滅。</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令每一個警員都被社會摒棄同孤立<br />\n作為社會一員，你有責任<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.做生意/開舖嘅你，今日起因行政理由，拒絕服務警員<br />\n<br />\n2. 有朋友親戚做黑警嘅話，同佢立即斷絕來往，並鼓勵其他朋友一同孤立黑警<br />\n<br />\n3. 一同向各國政府要求制裁香港警察<br />\n<br />\n既然大家武力不對等，就無謂再送頭，我地以社會壓力將呢群禽獸孤立起黎<br />\n呢個係作為一個人應有嘅基本良知同底線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NrSSWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NrSSWn.png&h=e8610c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6voZAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6voZAe.jpg&h=6ee10906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLasGOA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLasGOA.png&h=d0d7bf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEAgz8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEAgz8B.jpg&h=878bcd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHUk1OZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHUk1OZ.jpg&h=1a39d28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWxe6fF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%